@startuml
title Bieu do goi tong quan he thong

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

package "Thiet bi IoT" as IoT
package "Ung dung di dong" as Mobile
package "He thong may chu" as Backend
package "Co so du lieu" as Database
package "Dich vu MQTT" as MQTT
package "Dich vu thong bao" as Notification
package "Dich vu ban do" as Map

IoT ..> MQTT : Gui du lieu\nNhan lenh
Backend ..> MQTT : Tiep nhan du lieu\nGui lenh dieu khien
Mobile ..> Backend : API va du lieu thoi gian thuc
Backend ..> Database : Luu tru va truy van
Backend ..> Notification : Gui canh bao
Notification ..> Mobile : Push notification
Mobile ..> Map : Hien thi vi tri va hanh trinh

@enduml
